minggu depan, ya?

353
00:32:31,909 --> 00:32:33,118
Ya.

354
00:32:35,287 --> 00:32:38,999
Pater, aku akan sangat senang,
jika kau datang memberkati kami.

355
00:32:39,083 --> 00:32:40,668
Hei!

356
