00:52:08,042 --> 00:52:11,546
Kau mencari siapa?

526
00:52:13,297 --> 00:52:14,298
Apa kau kenal…

527
00:52:15,383 --> 00:52:16,676
Kang Chan-hee?

528
00:52:21,222 --> 00:52:22,265
Chan-hyeok…

529
00:52:24,517 --> 00:52:25,518
Apa kau…

